rows.label: qst103406_msg0001
rows.name:
It's good to see you're safe!
How did the mission go?

rows.label: qst103406_msg0002
rows.name:
So Akatsuki's Driver wasn't among
the Brionac leaders...

rows.label: qst103406_msg0003
rows.name:
No...there's no need for you to
worry yourselves any longer.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0004
rows.name:
I think it's time we withdrew
from this whole business.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0005
rows.name:
One of my subordinates who was
gathering intelligence for me has
been attacked.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0006
rows.name:
It may only be a matter of time before
they come after me or my son...

rows.label: qst103406_msg0007
rows.name:
But now that we've taken out the
leaders, Brionac's schemes will
fall apart sooner or later.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0008
rows.name: Ah, you're still worried about Akatsuki.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0009
rows.name:
But it would be far too dangerous
to pursue this any further...

rows.label: qst103406_msg0010
rows.name:
All right. But if you're going to keep
investigating, you'll have to do so alone.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0011
rows.name:
I can't provide you with any more
intelligence on Akatsuki or his Driver.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0012
rows.name: You'll have to find them by yourselves.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0013
rows.name:
I'm sorry. But when I think of my son,
this is the only choice I can...

rows.label: qst103406_msg0101
rows.name:
I'd appreciate it if you wouldn't
talk to me out in the open like this.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0102
rows.name:
You never know who might
be watching...
